prompt_text: Describe the scene of a flood.
content_text: Last few days, heavy rains caused a flood. After raining heavily and continuously for two days and night. My city became flooded. That the road leading to an out of the housing state where flooded too. I saw that many other local people were submerged in water. In fact the whole place looked like a lake. The people were carrying their luggage on the boats, luggage in the boat. In the morning, when the water level was just starting to write, children came out from their homes to play in the water. Many residents could not leave their homes to go to work. The development office.
